---
title: Indulgent Bacon & Mushroom Boscaiola with Garlic Panini
description: When the craving for a creamy pasta dish hits there’s only one solution - a boscaiola! Soft and warming, it will fill up your belly with love from the hearty mushrooms and bacon stirred through the sauce. Soak it up with a side of classic garlic bread.
